Method Detail

getOldValue

FlexfieldOldValueSupport.OldValue getOldValue(java.util.Map<java.lang.Byte,java.lang.Object> segmentInfo)
Returns the old value of a flexfield segment. The segment is identified by a collection of properties.

Parameters:
segmentInfo - the information of the segment. The keys are defined in this class as constants that have names starting with FOV_. Property FOV_SEGMENT_CODE is absent when the segment is the discriminator such as the context segment.
Returns:
